        <variablelist>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>WHAT?</term>
            <listitem>
              <para>
                By means of virtualization, you can run multiple virtual machines on a single
                bare-metal host.
              </para>
            </listitem>
          </varlistentry>
          <varlistentry>
            <term>WHY?</term>
            <listitem>
